#  Description: local include file 4xx_WME_LCL
#               Web Middleware Enablement
#               Web Administrators supporting WebSphere Application Server etc.
#  Software products and versions: WebSphere AppServer+ND, 8.x
#  Supported OS platforms: AIX, Linux
#  Owner: Thomas Seeling
#  Approval information: <reference>
